  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "To contact Handy customer service, you can use the following methods:\n\n1. **Phone Support**:  \n   - U.S. & Canada: 1-800-497-6332  \n   - UK: 020-3966-1607  \n   - Call during their operating hours for assistance.\n\n2. **Email Support**:  \n   - You can email Handy at **support@handy.com** for help with your inquiry or issue.\n\n3. **Live Chat**:  \n   - Visit the Handy website (www.handy.com) and look for the \"Help\" or \"Support\" section. There should be an option to initiate a live chat with a customer service representative.\n\n4. **Help Center**:  \n   - For self-service options and FAQs, visit **https://www.handy.com/help** to find answers to common questions.\n\n5. **App Support**:  \n   - If you use the Handy app, you can often access support through the app by navigating to the \"Help\" or \"Contact Us\" section.\n\nMake sure to have your booking details or account information ready when reaching out for faster assistance.",
